     <h2>
        About Spice Town Restaurants</h2>
    <p id="maindiv">
        Is your daily fare too bland and monotonous for you? Do yourself a favor and add
        some flavor in your eating routine. Come by Spice Town Restaurant. This place has
        an extensive menu which will surely add some much-needed zest in your meals. Expand
        your taste buds with a dash of paprika, a pinch of cayenne pepper and a sprinkle
        of ground dried chili. Spice Town Restaurant is a cafeteria-style restaurant that
        serves pizzas, pastas, burgers, salads, fried chicken, burritos, sandwiches, pitas,
        wings and subs. They have something for everyone! Whet your appetite with garlic
        bread and cheese, Cajun fries, chicken nuggets or Mozarrella sticks. For a hearty
        meal, you can choose from literally hundreds of items such as Turkey & Cheese and
        Roman Delight subs, Homemade Lasagna and Eggplant Parmesan Pasta or some good old
        fried chicken in different serving sizes. Halal meat is served upon request for
        most items on the menu. There are several dozen varieties of pizza. Take your pick
        from among gourmet selections like Taco, Fajita or Tandoori Chicken pizzas; or specialty
        items such as Spinach Delight, Napolitan, Vegetarian Delight, Bacon Cheeseburger
        and The Gladiator pizzas. The restaurant also has the familiar salad dishes like
        Caesar and Greek salads in their menu, as well as Mexican nachos and Greek pitas.
        You will love the hot Buffalo Wings with its spicy homemade ranch sauce, a favorite
        of many customers. Dessert is usually brownies, cheesecake, baklava or ice cream.
        Whether you want some spiced or spicy food, come to Spice Town Restaurant. Have
        lunch with your friends, or bring home some appetizing food for your loved ones.
    </p>
